koohiiStory1: Going, going, GONE!, said the gravedigger as he shoveled soil onto the body´s protruding elbow (the last bit left to cover).
koohiiStory2: If you want the soil stains gone from your clothes, then you´ll need to put some elbow grease into cleaning them.
